{"tid":319110,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣同人隱瞞自己家境","createTime":"2017-07-12T14:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T13:04:51.000Z","uid":41356,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56cdd848ca6d14a514a50560fbc457e23c0a915b","tid":319110,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"最近返緊暑假工，咁啲上咗年紀嘅清潔姐姐好撚八卦嘅<br />\n同佢傾多兩句偈就開始查我家宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿姐：喂𡃁仔你住邊頭㗎<br />\n我：乜乜站嗰頭啦<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：哦係咪XX花園呀<br />\n我：隔離個YY花園啦<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：嘩新樓喎，原來你咁有錢<br />\n我：都新咗幾年啦，係有錢就唔使出嚟返暑假賺錢啦，攤大手板咪有<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：你屋企&hellip;嗰時買幾錢呀<br />\n我：幾百萬掛，唔知喎我負責住嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿姐：幾多尺呀<br />\n我：幾百尺掛，點記得咁清楚，又唔係我買<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：幾多間房呀咁<br />\n我：(屌你老母答唔到唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) err...X間<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：嘩你老竇咁犀利呀，你實好開心啦屋企有層樓<br />\n我：唔犀利啦，咪又係打工仔一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿姐：咁都唔犀利？你層樓應該要XX萬喎？你由細到大都住私樓㗎？<br />\n我：唔係呀以前瞓天橋底，有巴士喇我要走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事實上好似係上咗年紀啲阿嬋先鐘意咁起人底，我已經估計到佢茶餘飯後會攞出嚟同人開心share，咩呀？是非當人情，秘密當手信呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n賽後檢討就係佢問我係咪XX花園嗰時，我就應該鳩答：「係呀，係嗰頭啦～」，然後再轉話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以有無又得體，又stop到佢嘅方法可以胡混過關呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa17b1c24d3df29cb0f41c4e31310a264f83ee0d","tid":319110,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"住屋村 完"},{"pid":"4a29112456cb329684746d721d231d704ebc9938","tid":319110,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"學識講大話<br />\n例如答佢住嗰頭啲公屋<br />\n答佢問題時有幾模糊就答幾模糊"},{"pid":"63b888847c6378023a9f30c98784f350341b31bb","tid":319110,"uid":7374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"睇黎你都幾後生 咩都答唔知 係掛咪得<br />\n金句 : 都係果啲 答完=無答<br />\n人地再問 姐係邊啲 照答 笑係果啲 人地就無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227f6d9e3db0bb4160a4f563542bf2dec7d10405","tid":319110,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:31:59.000Z","msg":"洶寶條車匙比佢睇下先"},{"pid":"b04d89668d63add5c8f9f6831528a37bb51fefba","tid":319110,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":27,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:32:15.000Z","msg":"我都試過同事問我住邊<br />\n我 : xxx 附近<br />\n佢: 即係邊到。<br />\n我:  xxx<br />\n佢 果到依家要二千幾万喎<br />\n我 甘上下啦<br />\n佢 咁你点解仲出来打工？<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08501eb90134c22b361498b0fc7791852f911771","tid":319110,"uid":56146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:32:27.000Z","msg":"出嚟做頭個幾日都係咁，之後發現唔對路先識敷衍佢哋，但已經自爆咗唔少嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dff6ebf51fef1758c492f9bc9576dd5cfaccec","tid":319110,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"阿嬸真係好鍾意查人家宅 下次答有幾模糊得咁模糊就得㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ceb7f3cdfeabbaea75a4198ba1e4bcd8c200e3c","tid":319110,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:36:29.000Z","msg":"次次答公屋,即刻唔再問你野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利伸:真係住公屋"},{"pid":"a9f5caddfbcb21a68b39b7c70fb0d61b76293a7b","tid":319110,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:38:18.000Z","msg":"循例問一問 一開頭啲icon有咩用<br />\n<br />\n答完佢附近啦 就應該搵機會走啦"},{"pid":"cd6ad9851a44301c2ae575a032ea90940c380c5b","tid":319110,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"嘩痴線 問得咁詳細<br />\n幫女搵老公都唔洗啦"},{"pid":"2624b64db52c5fe6f049691f725d0c3052c1ae4e","tid":319110,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>循例問一問 一開頭啲icon有咩用<br />\n<br />\n答完佢附近啦 就應該搵機會走啦</blockquote><br />\n今次我走得甩係因為我真係收工咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b64e7257e8d9c3d02f6a297b0ec2d0c1db72866","tid":319110,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:40:44.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母上維基睇下我嗰頭啲公屋資料先<br />\n記定一啲，下次邊個一問我就背返出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3bc2db130a3aa5742c7af038e6b1f267535455","tid":319110,"uid":41356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇黎你都幾後生 咩都答唔知 係掛咪得<br />\n金句 : 都係果啲 答完=無答<br />\n人地再問 姐係邊啲 照答 笑係果啲 人地就無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，係呢班人攪串個party<br />\n本來我覺得同事互相知下大家住邊無傷大雅，住得近嘅又傾得埋嘅，一齊收工咪一齊行囉（不論男女老少）<br />\n係都要問到篤又有乜為呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來都唔想呃人，大家識做咪算"},{"pid":"9451775f772cd0d16612e0bf5f045228f3545b9d","tid":319110,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"仲有班仆街知你屋企有錢<br />\n成日借啲兒食飯扮唔記得帶銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e491bfafdbac967b408e793becc76f81eb38752","tid":319110,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有班仆街知你屋企有錢<br />\n成日借啲兒食飯扮唔記得帶銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩邏輯嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人有錢，咁我問佢哋攞錢請你食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab13aae9cbcbf82916b1091706e0aed869c1a35","tid":319110,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有班仆街知你屋企有錢<br />\n成日借啲兒食飯扮唔記得帶銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩邏輯嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人有錢，咁我問佢哋攞錢請你食飯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係 女就無所謂 仔都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾撚厚面皮"},{"pid":"9160d99f8e3aac38edbcfc83760dc9f5ad38d61b","tid":319110,"uid":127789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住屋村 完</blockquote><br />\n住私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c731a8b8a23ef242d67538e2156d2fcab6c926aa","tid":319110,"uid":27129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"你答：我住喺你日日洗嘅公廁度喳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e0d3f48104397f4ce2e3e686c1b12d3d226b65","tid":319110,"uid":75522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"有啲阿姐問完會話介紹個女 / 親戚啲女你識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71529f837c7ae23dcfb936298af436d78a42e5f","tid":319110,"uid":76908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過同事問我住邊<br />\n我 : xxx 附近<br />\n佢: 即係邊到。<br />\n我:  xxx<br />\n佢 果到依家要二千幾万喎<br />\n我 甘上下啦<br />\n佢 咁你点解仲出来打工？<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢有冇話甘你老母？"},{"pid":"7472d1d098e1140375e32170f29069e372492a25","tid":319110,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T15:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都試過同事問我住邊<br />\n我 : xxx 附近<br />\n佢: 即係邊到。